<%# app/views/booking_mailer/payment_link.text.erb %>
Payment Reminder
=================

Dear <%= @booking.guest_name %>,

This is a reminder that you have an outstanding balance for your upcoming stay at The Anchorpoint Retreat.

Balance Due: <%= @balance_due %>

BOOKING SUMMARY
---------------
Confirmation: <%= @booking.confirmation_number %>
Check-in:     <%= @booking.check_in.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %>
Check-out:    <%= @booking.check_out.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y") %>

To pay your balance, visit: <%= @payment_url %>

If you have any questions, please reply to this email.

Warm regards,
The Anchorpoint Retreat Team

---
This email was sent to <%= @booking.guest_email %>.
